{"product_id":"ameerul-oud-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"Ameerul Oud Attar (Roll-On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol-Free","description":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover the rich, deep, and royal fragrance of Ameerul Oud Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis attar is crafted for those who love a strong, classy, and long-lasting oud fragrance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAmeerul Oud carries a bold aroma that is perfect for special occasions, prayers, and evening wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIts alcohol-free formula is skin-friendly and lets you experience the true depth and richness of oud.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: Oud \/ Woody\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll-On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol-Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStrong and long-lasting fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for both men and women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy Choose Ameerul Oud\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eRich and royal oud fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSmall quantity with powerful performance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStays for long hours\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eElegant packaging, perfect for gifting\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGently roll a small amount on your neck, wrists, or pulse points and enjoy a premium oud fragrance that lasts.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50471783891191,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/1FC990E2-B88B-47F2-8AB8-D82E2817ABB7.png?v=1777870289","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/ameerul-oud-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","provider":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","version":"1.0","type":"link"}